<item>
            <title>[SPR-8728] Support not (!) operator for profile selection</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-8728</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be really helpful if the profile attribute could take names of profiles that all has to be active.&lt;/p&gt;

